    Mai apni field ki bat karta hu-banking sector . Agar aaj thode bache Public Sector banks privatize kar diye jainge to sarkar ki 70% financial assistance aur finaicial inclusion schemes khatm ho jaigi...akele SBI se to hone se raha Aur private sector ka koi Bhi player rural non profitable branch chalne nahi dega. sara digitalization Aur make in India dhara rah jaiga.Aap ek bar public sector bank ki rural branch me jaiye Aur dekhiye ki sarkari employee kis had tak mehnat karte hain.....en banks ke jyadatar NPA bade corporate loans hain Jo pahle to govt push se disburse hue Aur ab default hone par RBI ne prudential write off karwa diya hai . enki B/S kharab honee me sarkar ka poora hath hai . es tarah apna stake Bech kar hath khade karne se nahi chalega...
